OL,3,CMum-of-three tried to take her own
OL,4,Clife after traumatic birth
OL,6,FDue to the difficult birth, Laura's
OL,7,Fson was very poorly when he was born
OL,8,Fand had to be taken by ambulance to
OL,9,FManchester Children's Hospital where
OL,10,Fhe had round the clock care.
OL,12,FBut within days of giving birth, Laura
OL,13,Ftried to take her own life.
OL,15,FShe said: "The midwife who found me
OL,16,Flooked horrified. I was told me that
OL,17,Fwhat was happening was, in some ways,
OL,18,Fa normal response to what had happened.
