OL,6,F"What happened to me was quite
OL,7,Fshocking. My brain had jumped to a
OL,8,Fshocking response."
OL,10,FConservative MP Theo Clarke gave an
OL,11,Femotional speech in the House of
OL,12,FCommons after she suffered a traumatic
OL,13,Fbirth.
OL,15,FLaura went on to have two other
OL,16,Fdistressing births with her daughter's
OL,17,FThea and Celia.
