OL,6,FShe is one of thousands of people who
OL,7,Fhave submitted their experiences of
OL,8,Fbirth trauma to a parliamentary
OL,9,Finquiry.
OL,11,FThe all-party inquiry is led by the
OL,12,FConservative MP, Theo Clarke, and
OL,13,FLabour's Rosie Duffield, and will look
OL,14,Finto the causes behind traumatic
OL,15,Fbirths.
OL,17,FClarke was inspired to take action
OL,18,Fafter needing emergency surgery and
OL,19,Fthinking she was going to die after
OL,20,Fthe birth of her daughter in 2022.
