OL,6,FThe parliamentary inquiry's aim is to
OL,7,Fdevelop policy recommendations to
OL,8,Freduce the rate of birth-related
OL,9,Ftrauma.
OL,11,FIt is open to parents and maternity
OL,12,Fprofessionals, with the findings
OL,13,Fexpected to be published by April 2024.
OL,15,F"The NHS is in crisis": Rachael
OL,16,FMcGrath speaks to Granada Reports
OL,17,Fpresenters Lucy Meacock and Andy
OL,18,FBonner about the public inquiry into
OL,19,Fbirth trauma
