OL,6,FRachael McGrath, the chair of Birth
OL,7,FTrauma Association, believes the
OL,8,Freason why some women experience
OL,9,Ftraumatic births is because the "NHS
OL,10,Fis in crisis".
OL,12,FShe said and the health service is
OL,13,Fstruggling to maintain maternity staff
OL,14,Fand "therefore services are getting
OL,15,Fmore difficult to provide."
OL,17,F"Women are coming into hospitals and
OL,18,Fasking for pain relief and there's no
OL,19,Fone there to administer it - and this
OL,20,Fis all helping to embed trauma",
OL,21,FRachel said.
