OL,6,FShe continued to say that the
OL,7,Fparliamentary inquiry has "opened
OL,8,FPandora's box" of years of birth
OL,9,Ftrauma events.
OL,11,F"An 84-year-old lady wrote in. She had
OL,12,Fa C-section more than 60 years ago
OL,13,Fwithout adequate anesthetic and has
OL,14,Fnever recovered."
OL,16,FMeanwhile, Rachel, who joined the BTA
OL,17,Fafter experiencing birth trauma, says
OL,18,Fsome women are terminating pregnancies
OL,19,Fbecause of distressing experiences
OL,20,Fthey have had in the past.
