OL,6,FShe said: "Nobody wants to make that
OL,7,Fdecision."
OL,9,FAn NHS spokesperson said: "The NHS is
OL,10,Fimproving our support to women who
OL,11,Fhave experienced a traumatic birth
OL,12,Fthrough rolling out specialist
OL,13,Fcommunity perinatal teams and offering
OL,14,Fcomprehensive postnatal check-ups.
