OL,6,F"But we understand there is more to
OL,7,Fdo, which is why the NHS is investing
OL,8,F#186 million to hire more midwives and
OL,9,Fother clinicians, backed by a three-
OL,10,Fyear delivery plan for maternity and
OL,11,Fneonatal services which will make care
OL,12,Fsafer and more personalised for women
OL,13,Fand babies."
OL,15,FMeanwhile, a Department of Health and
OL,16,FSocial Care spokesperson said: "We are
OL,17,Fcommitted to making the NHS the safest
OL,18,Fplace in the world to give birth, and
OL,19,Fthat's why birth trauma support is
OL,20,Famong the top priorities in the
OL,21,FWomen's Health Strategy in 2024.
